immunized almost 11000 a day die of dehydration caused by 
diarrhea and about 8000 a day of pneumonia 
the cost of immunizing all children and providing medication 
for dehydration and pneumonia is estimated to be about 25 billion 
a year it said adding such efforts could save 75 million 
children a year 
the report did not say how much now is spent on such 
immunization and medical care 
