of the spectrum that hubble cant touch said frank six a senior 
scientist at nasas marshall space flight center in huntsville ala 
one of its targets will be comet austin believed to be on its 
first trip through the solar system halleys comet would have been 
observed if astro had gone up as planned right after the 1986 
challenger mission that ended in tragedy 
